Package: gbifrules
Type: Package
Title: R Interface to GBIF Rule-Based Annotations Store
Version: 0.1.0
Author: John Waller <jwaller@gbif.org>
Maintainer: John Waller <jwaller@gbif.org>
Description: Provides R functions to facilitate interaction with the GBIF
  (Global Biodiversity Information Facility) rule-based annotation store. The
  package allows users to access, retrieve, and manage data utilizing the
  annotation store's data for analysis.
URL: https://github.com/gbif/occurrence-annotation, https://gbif.github.io/occurrence-annotation/gbifrules/
BugReports: https://github.com/gbif/occurrence-annotation/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
